MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

01-2093. State ex rel. J.H. Routh Packing Co. v. Erie Cty. Court of Common Pleas.

Eñe App. No. E-01-034. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Erie County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
